589
00:51:15,439 --> 00:51:19,273
Get out of here
with that damn trumpet!

590
00:51:27,117 --> 00:51:29,483
Come with me, sweet little head.

591
00:51:32,355 --> 00:51:34,550
Anita, come on.
Let's go to Mass.

592
00:51:47,437 --> 00:51:50,873
