- Yeah, but home first.

602
00:52:27,777 --> 00:52:30,302
- Okay, home first.
- And then we go swimming.

603
00:52:30,514 --> 00:52:33,779
- Then we go swimming.
- We'll all go together.

604
00:52:35,185 --> 00:52:39,019
- Who the hell are you? Who?
- It's me, Moraldo.

605
00:52:39,890 --> 00:52:44,850
No, you're nobody.
You're all nobodies.

606
00:52:48,665 --> 00:52:51,725
What do you think you're doing?

607
00:52:51,968 --> 00:52:55,927
- Nothing, nothing.
- You make me puke. Let me go.

608
00:52:56,139 --> 00:52:58,903
But Alberto, if I let you go...

609
00:52:59,109 --> 00:53:00,906
Let me go.
I wanna go by myself.

610
00:53:01,144 --> 00:53:04,272
- Alberto, you'll get hurt.
- I want to go alone. I'll be okay.

611
00:53:04,481 --> 00:53:05,505
You're nothing.

612
00:53:05,849 --> 00:53:09,148
- Alberto, look out, you'll fall.
- You make me puke.

613
00:53:09,753 --> 00:53:12,950
- Moraldo, please, let's go.
- I can't just leave him.

614
00:53:13,156 --> 00:53:15,886
May I come along now?
- Yeah, sure.

615
00:53:16,126 --> 00:53:17,286
Come on, come on.

616
00:53:17,894 --> 00:53:22,194
What do you want with me?
- Nothing. Just keep walking.

617
00:53:22,732 --> 00:53:24,393
Moraldo, know what?

618
00:53:26,670 --> 00:53:29,468
