633
00:54:18,154 --> 00:54:21,248
I can't just leave him.
You come too.

634
00:54:54,557 --> 00:54:57,754
Alberto, you're home.
Do you want me to take you in?

635
00:54:57,961 --> 00:55:00,429
I don't wanna go home.
What's there for me?

636
00:55:06,503 --> 00:55:08,994
I've been waiting for you.

637
00:55:09,205 --> 00:55:11,400
I wanted to say good-bye.

638
00:55:11,608 --> 00:55:14,441
I'm leaving, Alberto. Forgive me.

639
00:55:14,644 --> 00:55:17,044
I just couldn't take it anymore.

640
00:55:18,181 --> 00:55:19,978
Take care of Mama.

641
00:55:20,183 --> 00:55:22,174
I'll always think of you.

642
00:55:25,522 --> 00:55:26,614
Good-bye.

643
00:55:28,058 --> 00:55:29,889
Bye, Alberto.

644
00:55:35,665 --> 00:55:37,633
Try to be sensible, Alberto.

645
00:55:44,341 --> 00:55:47,208
Olga, where are you going?

646
00:55:48,511 --> 00:55:49,808
