00:57:35,718 --> 00:57:38,209
- What lady?
- That lady. Over there.

662
00:57:38,588 --> 00:57:40,419
Hello. May I help you?

663
00:57:40,623 --> 00:57:43,251
Two candles,
the kind I bought last year.

664
00:57:43,460 --> 00:57:45,792
I wasn't here last year.

665
00:57:45,995 --> 00:57:47,986
